review.body: Thank you very much for this PR, @pi-314159 ! This automates the build for both Windows and Linux significantly -- and brings the two instruction sets closer together. There's only two small comments for the main README.md that would be good to address to set user expectations suitably. Please also feel free to add Chromium to the main "oqs-demos" README.md table again as it obviously is an integration "alive" -- as documented by this PR.

pull_request.title: Use CMAKE_USE_PTHREADS_INIT
pull_request.body:
Precursor to #1549. Replace `OQS_USE_PTHREADS_IN_TESTS` with `CMAKE_USE_PTHREADS_INIT` to clean up the Threads inclusion and linking story.
